prompt:
An image of a woman standing gracefully in a serene, historic corridor with ornate marble pillars and an arched ceiling that shows signs of age and weathering. The background features lush green trees and foliage visible through the open sides of the corridor, adding a natural and tranquil ambiance. The woman is posed with a relaxed yet confident stance, leaning slightly against one of the marble pillars with her arms resting gently by her sides. She has wavy, shoulder-length dark hair and a calm, composed expression on her face.

She is wearing a sleeveless, light beige kurta adorned with a delicate floral pattern in shades of pink and green, featuring traditional motifs spaced evenly across the fabric. The kurta has a straight cut and falls just below the knees, paired with loose, light-colored palazzo pants that complement the kurta’s soft tones. On her feet, she wears matching pink embroidered slip-on sandals that echo the floral design of her kurta, adding a cohesive and elegant touch to her outfit. The overall look is simple yet sophisticated, blending traditional elements with a modern, effortless style.
